"shak. ant 2.6.78" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 6, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.2.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 2, 10</bibl> etc. After prepositions: <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.323" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 323</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.1.35" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 1, 35</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.663" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 663</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.2.75" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 2, 75</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.4.50" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 4, 50</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.1.102" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 102</bibl> etc. <emph>ye will</emph> contracted to <cit><quote>ye'll:</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 1.2.54" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 2, 54</bibl></cit> (Q<hi rend="sub">2</hi> Ff <emph>you'll</emph>). <emph>ye are</emph> contracted to <emph>y'are</emph> in O. Edd.: <bibl n="shak. aww 3.2.94" default="NO" valid="yes">All's III, 2, 94</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 3.7.14" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 7, 14</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.160" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 160</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.108" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 108</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.203" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 203</bibl> etc. In <bibl n="shak. per 2.1.60" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. II, 1, 60</bibl> Ff <emph>y'may see,</emph> Qq <emph>may see.</emph>
